# Frontend (Expo / React Native)

Follow [AGENTS.md](../AGENTS.md) and [frontend/AGENTS.md](../frontend/AGENTS.md). Do not assume — stop and ask the user if unsure. Update agent docs in the same change when frontend conventions or workflows change.

## Structure

- Screens in `app/` (expo-router); reusable UI in `components/`
- Use `@/` imports; API via `authenticatedFetch` from `@/lib/api/client`
- Auth via `useAuth()` from `@/contexts/AuthContext`

## Tests

- Co-locate `*.test.tsx`; mock AuthContext and api client
- BDD names: `given … when … then …`; optional Given/When/Then comments

## Config

- `EXPO_PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL` or `extra.apiUrl` — must match backend reachability (see development_faq for emulator/device)

